<section id="fs-id2416883" class="further-research" type="further-research">
<title>Further Research</title>
<para id="import-auto-id3112564">To learn more about population concerns, from the new-era ZPG advocates to the United Nations reports, check out the <link url="http://openstax.org/l/population_connection" window="new">Population Connection web site</link>.</para>
<para id="fs-idm405764272">Explore an interactive version of the <link url="http://openstax.org/l/2EDemoNow" window="new">population pyramid</link> for each country, and to see updates and changes over time: <link url="https://openstax.org/l/populationpyramid" window="new">at this website</link>.</para>
</section>
<section id="fs-id1503745" class="references" type="references">
<title>References</title>
<para id="fs-idm404724928">Budiman, Abby. 2020. “Key Findings About US Immigrants.” Pew Research Center. August 20, 2020. (https://www.pewresearch.org/fact-tank/2020/08/20/key-findings-about-u-s-immigrants/)</para>
